content:
Excellent idea on adding the "Program Since" column!

And, yes, you can definitely set up a reminder system within the spreadsheet to notify you when you're close to reaching a reward threshold. Here are a few ways to do it:

**Method 1: Conditional Formatting**

1. Add a new column, e.g., "Reward Threshold"
2. Enter the reward threshold value for each program (e.g., 200 stars for a free drink at The Daily Grind)
3. Use conditional formatting to highlight the row when the "Points/Balance" value is within a certain range of the reward threshold (e.g., 10-20 points away)
	* Format: `=AND(A2>=B2-20, A2<=B2)` (assuming Points/Balance in column A, Reward Threshold in column B, and you want to highlight when within 20 points of the threshold)

**Method 2: Custom Formula Alert**

1. Add a new column, e.g., "Alert"
2. Create a custom formula to check when the "Points/Balance" value is close to the reward threshold
	* Formula: `=IF(A2>=B2-20, "ALERT: Close to reward!", "")` (assuming Points/Balance in column A, Reward Threshold in column B, and you want to alert when within 20 points of the threshold)
3. Use this formula in the "Alert" column to display a message when the condition is met

**Method 3: Google Sheets Script (if you're using Google Sheets)**

1. Create a script that checks the spreadsheet for rows where the "Points/Balance" value is close to the reward threshold
2. Set up a trigger to run the script at regular intervals (e.g., daily or weekly)
3. Use the script to send you an email notification or create a notification in the spreadsheet when a reward threshold is approaching

Here's an example script:
```javascript
function checkRewardThresholds() {
  var sheet = SpreadsheetApp.getActiveSpreadsheet().getActiveSheet();
  var dataRange = sheet.getDataRange();
  var values = dataRange.getValues();

  for (var i = 1; i < values.length; i++) {
    var row = values[i];
    var points = row[2]; // assuming Points/Balance in column C
    var threshold = row[3]; // assuming Reward Threshold in column D
    var buffer = 20; // adjust the buffer value as needed

    if (points >= threshold - buffer && points <= threshold) {
      var message = "ALERT: You're close to a reward in " + row[0] + "!"; // assuming Program Name in column A
      MailApp.sendEmail("your_email@example.com", "Loyalty Program Alert", message);
    }
  }
}
```
Choose the method that works best for you, and you'll be notified when you're close to redeeming that free drink at The Daily Grind!
